    "description": "the truth is i haven‚Äôt been doing so well the last couple of weeks (or even months). it started with pain meds for migraines and my body completely freaking out on them. and wanting to be better soon, and working on ‚Äúfixing it‚Äù and rationalising the amount of time it would take to heal.\n\nit started with one doctor after the other not really knowing what it was or how to help, or even implying that i should just make more of an effort. with ER visits and blood tests and various types of meds and still being in pain every day \n\nall of this to say that i‚Äôm quite at the end of my strengths at the moment, both physically and emotionally. and that i‚Äôm not looking for advice i just want to keep you guys in the loop and be as open and honest as possible here. \n\ni notice how instagram isn‚Äôt feeling nourishing for me right now, how i feel a lot of pressure to create and do and be better already, how i get upset or angry being on here (and i definitely don‚Äôt want to be that kind of person) so i‚Äôve decided to take some distance here. i only want to show up here when i actually have the energetic capacity to hold you guys and share, not because i feel like i have to for engagement. there won‚Äôt be any offerings in october either, i really have to focus on getting better first.",
