    "filename": "2021-09-29_2673511984370281644.jpg",
    "description": "ìäì musings on the energy of this moment ìäì\n\nit feels so urgent, the energy right now, the massive built up and all these stray whispers. it‚Äôs electric. and at the same time we‚Äôre not there yet, it‚Äôs close but not yet (i feel like i‚Äôve been saying this for ever). \n\nwe are edging closer but we are not there and all we can do now is sit back and settle in. let ourselves be carried, allow ourselves to feel whatever we have to feel about that.\n\nremind ourselves that we don‚Äôt have to do anything and we are where we are supposed to be.\n\nwe are in transit and the fact is that we always are and life is learning to be okay with that. taking care of ourselves while things are shifting, creating safe spaces for us to retreat into when things (and the world) get crazy.\n\nthis is the lesson, this is what self care and energy work is really about, there will always be something that‚Äôs ‚Äúnot yet‚Äù or not where we want it to be or that‚Äôs shifting. that‚Äôs how this is supposed to go, that is life. \n\nas soon as we accept that that is what it‚Äôs about, that we will never really be done, we can start to focus on the real things. how can we keep ourselves safe and sane in transit? how can we make sure our bodies and nervous systems are nourished and solid? what are we learning and unlearning?\n\nlet go and lean in babies, we are preparing to dive a little deeper again this season\n\n_\n#energymusings #oracle #channeledmessage #cyclicalliving #embodied #lifelessons #change #becoming #darkmoon #soulful #embodiedtarot #healing #whatspiritualityis #softening",
    "likes": 67,
