    "post_id": "2733728097553911300",
    "filename": "2021-12-21_2733728097553911053.jpg",
    "description": "i wanted to do a winter solstice post, with some rituals or tips or something like that and then i realised those kind of things don‚Äôt feel right anymore. they don‚Äôt feel right for me anymore. they don‚Äôt feel right for us as a collective anymore.\n\nwe haven‚Äôt been through this whole hierophant, intense shadow phoenix year for others to tell us what is suitable, for me to tell you what to do. it doesn‚Äôt fit anymore, it hasn‚Äôt been fitting for quite some time but after this year that is completely over. it doesn‚Äôt take into account that your experience and my experience are not the same and we have soft, knowing cores of our own.\n\nthe hierophant - 5th card of the major arcana and card of the year for 2021 - has been, not so gently, urging us to step into ourselves, to trust our own intuition, create our own rituals and magic and groundwork. there isn‚Äôt any right or wrong when it comes to these things, just what calls you, what feel right and accessible and joyful for the version for you at this moment. \n\nso basically i want to invite you to do you. to trust that the perfect ritual for this solstice is the one that pops up while you are reading this or has been popping up for you the past few days.\n\ntwo gentle reminders in that regard. remember that everything is a ritual. that you are an animal and that animals crave warmth and nourishment and safety and rest\n\nhappy winter solstice babes, it only going to get lighter from here on out\n_\n#wintersolstice #oracle #ritual #void #portal #hierophantenergy #sovereign #intuition #reclamation #becoming #beyourownguru #softanimal #soften #altarwork #sacredspace #empowerment #embodiedtarot #tarotteacher #witchythings #napfluencer",
