    "description": "living and loving for this season \n\nthe softest afternoon sunlight and all the rainbows it magically conjures up in our living room. mornings spent on the shaggy rug in front of my altar with a candle and lemon water. drinking cinnamon coffee with whipped cream on our front steps and soaking in the sunshine after lunch. all the writing and reading and musing. listening to tarot lectures and talking on podcasts. dreaming about writing my own book. wearing glitter on my eyes and velvety dresses the colour of wine. going for take out coffee and sticky buns and taking pictures of every flower in de kruidtuin and calling it an adventure. making cosy spots all over the house and using all the pillows and blankets, gathering all the candles and fairy lights. the cats napping as close as possible, always a tail or a paw or a bun resting on me, purring. waking up at night with one cat at my feet and one in the crook of my arm and your hand resting on my arm.\n\nmore, more of this please\n_\n#lifewithcancer #thisiswhatcancerlookslike #adventure #soften #magic #healing #soften #kruidtuin #coffee #fairylights #thelittlethings #rituals #catlover #moonchild #alive #chronicillness #incurableillness #bowelcancer #braf",
