    "post_id": "2778615378929155000",
    "filename": "2022-02-21_2778615378929155257.mp4",
    "description": "i can feel a million different versions of me whispering musings \n\nìè≤\n\ni don‚Äôt really have a lot of words this week, just incomplete thoughts and vague whispers in the wake of wednesday‚Äôs full moon. the first full moon that i‚Äôve felt this profoundly, that i felt like i used to ‚Äúbefore‚Äù. sitting next to the veil and letting my fingers rest on it. being my oracle self, former self. well enough and strong enough and healthy enough to be in this energy, to be more than just a sick body. channeling and humming and being in it.\n\na saturday adventure exploring beautiful Leuven, we technically do not live in the city anymore and it was my first time taking the bus since forever and in a way it made me feel like we were on a trip exploring a city we‚Äôd never been to before. exploring with fresh eyes meeting layers and layers of our history there, together and apart. treasuring adventure and beautiful things.\n\ncooking myself dinner a few evenings in a row, just the fact of being able to do that. zucchini and chickpeas and rice, soy sauce and lime and chili. the way i have been feeding myself for ages, when i lived by myself, before meal plans and before not being able to eat any of that for months and before not being able to cook for myself\n\ni‚Äôm not the me from before, i will never be the me from before and i don‚Äôt want to be. pieces of myself i never thought i would find again are returning to me, colliding into me. im not the me from before but more and more i am starting to feel there will be a me after, that she is almost here. \n_\n#becoming #oracle #moonchild #fullmoon #ritual #embodied #lifeisaritual #creatingbeauty #soften #visitleuven #whatcancerlookslike #blueskies #mucha #ankh #rest #selfcare",
    "likes": 65,
