    "description": "i‚Äôm sitting in the hammock we (aka my dad) hung up in our gorgeous tree today, basking in the evening sunlight, looking at the gorgeous flowers around me, musing about the simple magic of this. today we went to the garden centre to pick out some flowers and i also got a eucalyptus plant because i‚Äôve been wanting one for ages, so i have my own supply to set inside in vases and burn at my altar. it‚Äôs sitting in a pot that used to belong to my grandpa, standing on my porch, it‚Äôs so simple and so meaningful. to be able to connect to my heritage in this way, remembering the summers spent at my grandpa‚Äôs place, picking cherries, wandering through his enormous garden that was like a fairy forest and our playground, not realising what a treasure that is. spending time in my dad‚Äôs garden and taking picture of all the trees, picking flowers to dry in between my books, sitting on the grass and now seeing him work so hard on this little garden, pouring some of his heart in magic in here as well.\n\ni can‚Äôt even begin to explain how happy this makes me, this garden, connecting with the plants and flowers and joy that comes with it. testing out my own green fingers that‚Äôs bringing back all these memories from these men in my life, celebrating and creating life\n_\n#homing #slowlife #heritage #moonchild #gardenlove #soften #becoming #spring #newlife #eucalyptus #magic #wonder #lineage #ancesteralhealing",
