    "description": "one of my favourite rituals we have as a couple are our ‚Äúeurovison weekends‚Äù, it started as a trip that happened to be during the eurovison song contest and the joke that we should make it an annual thing. 6 years later it is one of our long standing rituals and the one i love most. every year we book a hotel, get a lot of snacks and watch the contest on (mostly weird and/or small) tv sits in hotel beds. one year we even managed to book a hotel without a tv, good thing it‚Äôs not really about the contest but mostly about the adventure \n\nlast year we went to brussels as well but i wasn‚Äôt really capable of doing anything but taking a bath and taking lots of naps, this year we also got to explore, eat good food, take a lot of pictures and we went on a tipsy shopping spree when i had about half of a mojito. i did have a couple of crashes and my back is killing me right now but i‚Äôm still sitting here with huge smile. we were able to continue our tradition for another year (last year i was really anxious it would be my last one) and we had such fun exploring and basking in the sunshine and the beauty\n_\n#bruxellesmabelle #tradition #ritual #thisiswhatcancerlookslike #wanderer #travelgram #eurovision #hotellife #soften #bowelcancer #adventure #artdeco #loveroflight #photgrapher #oracle",
