    "description": "‚âò gentle reminder ‚âò\n\na prayer, an incantation\na softening\na cocoon\na safe and sacred space\nof surrender\nand lessons of undoing and \nnot doing \n\n‚âò\n\nthis eclipse season we are in is all about softening and leaning into it. this is not the time to work with energy and ‚Äúmanifest‚Äù and do rituals or magic. this is energy that is helping you shift and also an ultimate lesson in not doing \n\nso if, like me, you have been feeling like you are not doing the full moon right because you are not doing anything, guess what, you are doing it exactly right\n\nthis is the time to cocoon and fold down into yourself. to focus on taking exquisite care of yourself. rest. nourish. ground. \n\nallow the energy to unfold. allow yourself to do less. notice what that brings up about about worth and shoulds and grief and restlessness. let go and then let go some more. know that these are exactly the lessons you are meant to dive into right now \n\n#eclipseseason #eneegyreport #channeledmessage #oracle #soften",
