    "filename": "2022-05-20_2842420798011876131.jpg",
    "description": "this eclipse season has been a portal for me back into my channel/connection/empress + oracle vibes\n\ni have lost a deep part of my cyclicalness and creativity when i lost my cycle. of course menstruation is not the only thing that connects us to our own sacredness and fluidity but for me it had always been my main pathway and then it was gone. and i was too sick and busy finding other things. so i waited and i lost it and i was not so patient. slowly, when i had the space for it and it started feeling safe again, it came back to me. in the form of my garden, in the form of tarot, in the form of dreams and channelings and poetry and beauty and writing. this eclipse season was the push that birthed me through the last pieces of resistance.\n\ni‚Äôm back in sync, in the flow of things. the moon speaks to me again (i mean she never stopped but i wasn‚Äôt able to hear). leaning back into archetypes i though i had lost and buried for ever\n\nìäì\n\noracle\nchannel\nwoman\nwitch\nmuse\npoet\n\nìäì\n#eclipsemusings #becoming #journal #moonchild #oracle #channel #archetypes #shadowwork #healing #evolution #energeticupgrades #energyreport #embodied",
