    "description": "the biggest compliment i get is when people tell me something i created has allowed them to discover beauty, especially when it‚Äôs in a place where they thought there wasn‚Äôt any\n\nthat‚Äôs why i take picture of the everyday. cups of coffee and tea and flowers in varying states of bloom. the light, always the most gorgeous light. kittens. cosy spots i created and pretty things i discovers in my home or my garden or my city. that‚Äôs why i write about wonder and amazement and beauty in the mondain. of living in a body. in this world.\n\nbecause all these things are profoundly beautiful to me, i am very much a ‚Äúlook at the moon/look at the sky/oh that‚Äôs a cat‚Äù kind of person. the person that is looking for seashells whenever she visits the ocean. when we visited the ancient sites in cyprus i was always torn because there where these ruins and also cats and also a view at the ocean and also all these cool plants. i didn‚Äôt know where to look or focus because everything was wonderful to me.equally filled with wonder.\n\nit fills my heart with so much joy when i can get someone to seethe world the way i see it, even for a little while\n_\n#oracle #beauty #embodied #reflector #photography #travelgram #islandlife #creatrix #moonchild #mermaid #soften #becoming #embodied #livinginabody #seetheworldthrougmyeyes #wonder #sacredsites #ritual #creationasaritual #treasures #magpie #sings #intuitiveliving #cyclicalliving #temple",
