    "filename": "2022-07-06_2876505686508163663.jpg",
    "description": "the world feels like an exceptionally heartbreaking place right now\n\nradiant, vibrant\nwild, filled with wonder \nfilled with grief and loss\n\ni can feel fear hooking its fingers under my clavicle. a tenderness in the pit of my stomach. tension in my whole being. and i know i‚Äôm not the only one.\n\nhere are a few things i like to remind myself when it feels like the bottom has dropped our from under everything and i want to share with you + some wonder in the form of words (@tessguinery has been a saviour) and images and beauty that might help us let in a little bit of light again\n\n_\n\nhere is what i want you to know\n\nif the world feels like it‚Äôs too much and not enough at the same time you are not \nalone\n\nif it feels like you cannot possible take a deep breath in because of all the weight and tension you have been feeling in your chest, you can, it will be hard at first and then it will get a bit easier and there will still be tension and tears but it will be a bit softer and that is enough \n\nknow that you are not alone. know that there is still beauty and grace and softness around the corner. know that you are strong and resilient and vulnerable and safe.\n_\n#gentlereminder #mentalhealth #youaresafe #lifewithcancer #thisiswhatcancerlookslike #incurableillness #embodied #soften #trauma #thereisbeautyhere #channel #hope #theapricotmemoirs #healingwords #photography",
