    "description": "Part 2 - i wanted to part with some words of wisdom or whatever so fittingly this will be my last gentle reminder. \n\nwe need your kind of magic in this world. whatever it is, whatever that looks like. even more so when it doesn‚Äôt look or feel like magic or anything special to you! when you feel like you don‚Äôt really have a talent or anything important to offer to the world, this message is even more important and very sneakkily especially meant for you. i can see your magic. i know, feel, swear that you are making a difference in this world just by being in it. please continue to shine your light.\n\nplease be gentle with yourself. the world is so hard and life can be heavy and a lot and the times are really really transformative (which we all know is just a nice word for f*cking hard). show yourself grace and kindness through all this. allow yourself to feel and rest and have bad days. become an expert in taking care of yourself, knowing the signs of your body when you need some extra down time, knowing what gives you energy and what inspired you. \n\nplease lean in and listen to the little voice inside of you and follow their call and directions. you know. you really do. everything is already in you, that‚Äôs not the work you have to do here. the work is allowing yourself to listen to it. making sure it feels safe to follow the little whispers that make absolutely no sense at the moment but will in time. this is the most important job you have here, allowing yourself to lean into what you already know and follow it and making it feel as safe and easy as possible.",
